data.description: New Price!!! Welcome to this charming townhouse with an abundance of natural light and delightful features. This cozy abode offers a spacious 1336 square feet of living space, providing comfort and style for your everyday living. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere. The living areas are generously bathed in sunlight, creating a cheerful and welcoming environment. The sunroom off the back of the home serves as a serene retreat, perfect for relaxation, reading, or enjoying your morning coffee in a tranquil setting. Step outside to your private patio, a small oasis where you can savor the outdoors, entertain guests, or cultivate a beautiful garden. This outdoor space offers a seamless extension of your living area and is an ideal place for outdoor gatherings. In addition to the captivating interior and outdoor spaces, you'll also benefit from private parking, ensuring convenience and security.
